modules.source:
"mixin head()
  head
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='author', content='Aleksei and Maria Arro')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, shrink-to-fit=no')
    meta(http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible', content='ie=edge')
    title #{pageTitle}

    - const { fonts } = require('@/json/fonts.json');
    - for (const { fileNameBase, sets } of fonts)
      - for (const { weight, style } of sets)
        link(
          rel='preload',
          href=require(`@/fonts/${fileNameBase}_${weight}_${style}.woff2`).default,
          as='font',
          crossorigin='anonymous',
        )
"
